                "type": "source_text",
                "content": "Prototyping is often used to design a good user interface : the part of the system with which the user interacts.",
                "img_id": null
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "role": "sentence",
        "segment": "and it can bring to the surface issues and assumptions that may not have been clear using other approaches to requirements analysis.",
        "citations": [
            {
                "type": "source_text",
                "content": "Since the user interface is, in a sense, a bridge between the application domain and the software development team, prototyping can bring to the surface issues and assumptions that may not have been clear using other approaches to requirements analysis.",
                "img_id": null
